# Phase Readiness Checklist (Chat Gate)

Before implementation starts for any phase, post a short checklist message in chat confirming:

- Phase documents reviewed
- Completed-phase code reviewed
- Plan mode used and implementation plan prepared
- Ready to begin implementation

Implementation should start only after this checklist message is posted, unless the user explicitly asks to skip it.
